Trigger:
    - Clear ALL Connected: Ctrl+L
    - Remove selected: Ctrl+D
    - Assign New: Ctrl+A
    - Assign tracking enemy: Ctrl+Q
    - Change locked cam position: Ctrl+R
    
Enemy:
    - Toggle shoot blocker change direction : Ctrl+F ; Ctrl+G
    - Sword kill speed modifier change : Ctrl+O ; Ctrl+P
    
Environment:
    - Propeller power change : Ctrl+Q ; Ctrl+E
    - Door trigger : Ctrl+T
    - Move sequence add/remove/clear : Ctrl+N ; Ctrl+M ; Ctrl+C
